name: Hazaq- Be Strong
description:
20 year Old Jessica Morris has released her first EP, 'Hazaq: Be Strong.' Featuring Seven Tracks all written or co written by Jessica,  the tracks range from the lyrical significance of 'By Grace,' to the fun of 'A Jonas Brother' Featuring BeaMed. Buy your copy today and experience the hope and joy of her music!

To preview the album go to www.myspace.com/jessicamorrismusic

Order your copy TODAY for $AU10 + P/H
